---
import Layout from "../layouts/BasicLayout.astro";
import ResumeComponent from "../experiments/ResumeComponent.astro";
---

<Layout pageName="resume" title="Kabir's Resume">
	<div class="mainBody">
		<div class="myStory text-white">
			<div class="myStoryHeader">My Programming Journey</div>

			<div class="myStoryText mb-8">
				My introduction to programming was with Logo's turtle, guiding the little triangle around the screen to draw geometric patterns. It was a couple years later that I learned about the more general uses of programming, my godfather gifted me a copy of Micheal Dawson's <a href="https://www.amazon.ca/Python-Programming-Absolute-Beginner-Third/dp/1435455002" class="link">Python Programming for the Absolute Beginner.</a> The book taught me the basics of logic and code, in my zeal, I tried making a game with just conditionals and loops, all on the terminal, I gave up a little while after when I got tied of copy-pasting my changes into each of the four game modes (my naive self had to learn about functions and other abstractions). I have since built many projects in many more languages and contexts. I have written web apps, CLI tools, robotics software and everyday I'm trying to learn more. 
				My goals now are to learn more about the theory of computation and lower level programming.

				<div class="leaveAReview mt-4">
					<a href="https://reviewkit.me/review/Sq3_qcXJwnv" class="link leaveAReviewHeader" target="_blank">
						<div class="leaveAReviewHeader">Leave a Review!!</div>
					</a>

					<div class="leaveAReviewText">
						I'd love to hear your thoughts, always looking for ways to improve!
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="resume">
			<div class="fileLink link text-white mb-4">
				<a href="/resume.pdf" title="Link to pdf file" target="_blank">
					My resume
				</a>
			</div>
			<embed class="resumeEmbed" src="/resume.pdf" type="application/pdf" />
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
	.mainBody {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		justify-content: space-between;
		width: 100%;
		min-height: 70vh;
		margin-top: 1%;

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			flex-direction: column;
			justify-content: flex-start;
		}
	}

	.link {
		color: #6e6ed7;
		transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
		&:hover {
			transform: scale(1.2);
			color: #fff;
		}
	}

	.myStoryHeader {
		font-size: 2em;

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			font-size: 1.5em;
		}
	}

	.myStory {
		padding-top: 3%;
		width: 60%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			width: 100%;
			order: 1;
			font-size: 0.75em;
			padding-top: 3vh;
		}
	}

	.myStoryText {
		font-size: 1.25em;

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			font-size: 1em;
		}
	}

	.leaveAReview {
	}

	.leaveAReviewHeader {
		width: 50%;
		font-size: 1.25em;

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			width: 100%;
			order: 2;
		}
	}

	.leaveAReviewText {
		font-size: 1em;
	}

	.resume {
		flex-grow: 1;
		height: 100%;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.resumeContainer {
		height: 100%;
		transform: translateY(-5%);
	}

	.fileLink {
		font-size: 2.5em;

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			font-size: 1.5em;
		}
	}

	.resumeEmbed {
		min-height: 55vh;
		width: 80%;
		background-color: #f5f5f5;
		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			height: 70vh; 
		}
	}
</style>
